<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- man̊ yuṣalĩy mū̊̉minaⁿạ
 bīasūʿa lạa yakẖīb̊
 biạs̊mihi ạlậbu lanā
 kulã ḥīniⁿ yas̊tajīb̊

[C1]
   ạlqrạr: yas̊tajību yas̊tajīb̊
   yas̊tajību ṭālibīh̊
   laẘ tāảnãy̱ yas̊tajīb̊
   mun̊ṣifaⁿạ limukẖ̊tārīh̊

[V2]
 2- ạis̊ạảlūạ min̊hu tuʿ̊ṭaẘạ
 fah̊wa yuʿ̊ṭī man̊ qaṣad̊
 wāṭ̊lubūạ fatajidūạ
 kulũ man̊ yaṭ̊lub̊ yajid̊

[V3]
 3- ạiq̊raʿūạ ạl̊bāba ạlrãfīʿ̊
 fah̊wa yaf̊taḥu lakum̊
 ại̹nãhu ạlậbu ạlsãmīʿ̊
 yaʿ̊lamu ạḥ̊tīājakum̊

[V4]
 4- ạiṭ̊raḥūạ ạl̊ḥim̊la ʿalaẙh
 min̊ balạyā wahumūm̊
 man̊ ạảtay̱ ḥubaⁿ̃ạ ại̹laẙh
 nāla min̊hu mā yarūm̊

[V5]
 5- fal̊natẖiq̊ fī waʿ̊di ạlậb̊
 biại̹ymāniⁿ rāsikẖīn̊
 hakadẖā qāla ạl̊kitāb̊:
 &quot;man̊ waʿad̊ hūa ạảmīn̊&quot;</lyrics>
<title>mn yṣly mw̉mnạ</title>
<author>ạbrạhym nạṣyf ʿṭyẗ</author>
</song>